description: Federation ops console when editing ops files
globs: ops/**
alwaysApply: false
---

When working under `ops/`, this is the IWGF ops console (ops.iwgf.org) for Warp + Lattice. Use the header **Warp | Lattice** product toggle — shared panels reuse chrome; Crews/Reports/TTS hide on Lattice. Warp + Lattice **ops** callables live in `Warp12/functions` (same `/api/fn` proxy). Lattice **player** callables stay in `subspace-lattice/apps/functions`. Deploy stages through `Warp12/federation-hosting/ops`.

See root `AGENTS.md` and `ops/README.md`.
